						<summary>

						<p>On the same rock in the Tirunātharkuṉṟu near the village.</p>						

						<p>This inscription engraved in very early characters (See Introduction) records the fast unto death in 57 days, by Chandiranandi Āśirigar (Āśiriyar) at this place.</p>						

